<H3><FONT COLOR="#FF0000"><BLINK>Who Am I?</BLINK> </FONT></H3>

<P>I am a faculty member in the <!WA2><A HREF="http://www.cs.jhu.edu">Department
of Computer Science </A>, Johns Hopkins University. I am also a member
of the <!WA3><A HREF="http://www.ece.jhu.edu/~clsp/">Center for Language and
Speech Processing </A>here at Hopkins. My research interests include natural
language processing, spoken language systems, machine learning and artificial
intelligence. My e-mail address is <B><!WA4><A HREF="mailto:brill@cs.jhu.edu">brill@cs.jhu.edu</A></B> I look nothing like that picture. Not yet, at least. 
</P>

<P>
<HR WIDTH="100%">
<HR WIDTH="100%">
<HR WIDTH="100%"></P>

